{"tid":2084479,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港交所縮短牛熊証等產品上市周期至3個交易","createTime":"2020-06-29T09:07:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T10:36:02.000Z","uid":25473,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b89ddf594c89356eb07c15dc847c168e3e269c56","tid":2084479,"uid":25473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T09:07:27.000Z","msg":"港交所縮短牛熊証等產品上市周期至3個交易<br />\n<br />\n港交所公布，將結構性產品的上市周期，由5個交易日縮短至3個交易日，發行商在提交產品條款之後的第3個交易日，就可以將結構性產品，例如衍生權證、牛熊證及界內證於現貨市場上市，新上市周期適用於下月13日或之後推出的產品。港交所市場主管姚嘉仁表示，更短的結構性產品上市周期，有助發行商更好應對市場狀況變化，提高市場效率，又指今次決定是進一步發展，並優化結構性產品市場的重要一步。<br />\n<br />\n2020-06-29 17:01:24<br />\n<br />\nSource: Rthk <br />\n<br />\n全亞洲最大賭場真係多野玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30631084e454b24ce29bd08ec666670f8fba58d1","tid":2084479,"uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T09:09:41.000Z","msg":"垃圾，連周結期權都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5e4eeef7793aa0ff68dab09376658bd447e253f","tid":2084479,"uid":244394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"賭咩場 個市造出來既 大户睇住來食既"},{"pid":"625edacb8b00f80a2900fc9c8faf5515080cbe2c","tid":2084479,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T09:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac238b69276d98d78b86becbf08258eebdfa7fa3","tid":2084479,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T09:11:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">你哋班連登仔， 喺連登圍爐洗版有撚用？</span><br />\n<br />\n我要見到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">IG Facebook</span>  各大社交平台<br />\n都要見到呢幾隻字<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>7月1 維園見</strong></span></span><br />\n<img